(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 228.6 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid de7365e8-6302-58bb-88cc-8142bd7042b5))
(text "J30 is the outside-world HDMI jack. The retired Intehill controller is a bench-test/fallback fixture, not motherboard circuitry." (at 20.32 236.22 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ab256c5f-ccad-53b8-8805-a50520eea80f))
(text "TMDS ESD uses 0.15pF-max, +/-3.6V TPD1E0B04DPLR single-line parts; route each shunt at J30 with no stub." (at 20.32 243.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 29c03f97-3db4-5b7d-ba0d-b318e9429fb1))
(text "CEC and utility are explicitly NC; unused TPD13S523 legacy channels use the datasheet 75R-to-GND termination." (at 20.32 251.46 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ef1d7178-5ceb-5f45-8815-a37d569c5c53))
(text "U54/U55 remove 5V/DDC/HPD power while the Mu is off; PCA9306 translates DDC/SCDC and U53 buffers HPD." (at 20.32 259.08 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 38aa3fef-f0aa-55ad-8fa8-22a49504c81b))
(text "Release gate: verify >=4.8V at J30 pin 18 under 55mA and validate the finished 100-ohm HDMI 2.0 layout on hardware." (at 20.32 266.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 2bd5c9db-a3ac-563a-a325-87d2cac8d2b5))
